0.title: About
0.body:
[b]ABOUT VITICULTURE:[/b]

In [b][i]Viticulture[/i][/b], the players find themselves in the roles of people in rustic, pre-modern Tuscany who have inherited meager vineyards. They have a few plots of land, an old crushpad, a tiny cellar, and three workers. They each have a dream of being the first to call their winery a true success.

The players are in the position of determining how they want to allocate their workers throughout the year. Every season is different on a vineyard, so the workers have different tasks they can take care of in the summer and winter. There's competition over those tasks, and often the first worker to get to the job has an advantage over subsequent workers.

Fortunately for the players, people love to visit wineries, and it just so happens that many of those visitors are willing to help out around the vineyard when they visit as long as you assign a worker to take care of them. Their visits (in the form of cards) are brief but can be very helpful.

Using those workers and visitors, players can expand their vineyards by building structures, planting vines (vine cards), and filling wine orders (wine order cards). Players work towards the goal of running the most successful winery in Tuscany.

Wait.time(
    function()
        if CURRENT_SEASON == "Spring" and PASSING == false then
            if (
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow") and checkCockSide(yellowCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue") and checkCockSide(blueCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green") and checkCockSide(greenCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red") and checkCockSide(redCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White") and checkCockSide(whiteCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange") and checkCockSide(orangeCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange"))
            ) then
                broadcastToAll("All players chosen their wake up time.\nIt is Summer, place your workers!")
                CURRENT_SEASON = "Summer"
            end
        end
        if CURRENT_SEASON == "Summer" and PASSING == false then
            if (
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow") and checkCockSide(yellowCock) == "Right" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue") and checkCockSide(blueCock) == "Right" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green") and checkCockSide(greenCock) == "Right" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red") and checkCockSide(redCock) == "Right" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White") and checkCockSide(whiteCock) == "Right" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange") and checkCockSide(orangeCock) == "Right" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange"))
            ) then
                broadcastToAll("All players have passed.\nIt is Fall, draw your visitor cards!")
                CURRENT_SEASON = "Fall"
                if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow") then
                    yellow_player_hand_count_on_fall = #(Player["Yellow"].getHandObjects())
                end
                if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue") then
                    blue_player_hand_count_on_fall = #(Player["Blue"].getHandObjects())
                end
                if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green") then
                    green_player_hand_count_on_fall = #(Player["Green"].getHandObjects())
                end
                if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red") then
                    red_player_hand_count_on_fall = #(Player["Red"].getHandObjects())
                end
                if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White") then
                    white_player_hand_count_on_fall = #(Player["White"].getHandObjects())
                end
                if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange") then
                    orange_player_hand_count_on_fall = #(Player["Orange"].getHandObjects())
                end
            end
        end

        if CURRENT_SEASON == "Fall" then
            if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow") then
                yellow_player_hand_count_on_fall_after = #(Player["Yellow"].getHandObjects())
            end
            if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue") then
                blue_player_hand_count_on_fall_after = #(Player["Blue"].getHandObjects())
            end
            if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green") then
                green_player_hand_count_on_fall_after = #(Player["Green"].getHandObjects())
            end
            if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red") then
                red_player_hand_count_on_fall_after = #(Player["Red"].getHandObjects())
            end
            if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White") then
                white_player_hand_count_on_fall_after = #(Player["White"].getHandObjects())
            end
            if isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange") then
                orange_player_hand_count_on_fall_after = #(Player["Orange"].getHandObjects())
            end
            if(
                (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow") and (yellow_player_hand_count_on_fall_after > yellow_player_hand_count_on_fall) or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow")) and
                (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue") and (blue_player_hand_count_on_fall_after > blue_player_hand_count_on_fall) or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue")) and
                (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green") and (green_player_hand_count_on_fall_after > green_player_hand_count_on_fall) or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green")) and
                (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red") and (red_player_hand_count_on_fall_after > red_player_hand_count_on_fall) or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red")) and
                (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White") and (white_player_hand_count_on_fall_after > white_player_hand_count_on_fall) or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White")) and
                (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange") and (orange_player_hand_count_on_fall_after > orange_player_hand_count_on_fall) or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange"))

            ) then
                broadcastToAll("All players have drawn their visitor cards.\nIt is Winter, place your workers!")
                CURRENT_SEASON = "Winter"
            end
        end

        if CURRENT_SEASON == "Winter" and PASSING == false then
            if (
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow") and checkCockSide(yellowCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Yellow")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue") and checkCockSide(blueCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Blue")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green") and checkCockSide(greenCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Green")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red") and checkCockSide(redCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Red")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White") and checkCockSide(whiteCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"White")) and
            (isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange") and checkCockSide(orangeCock) == "Left" or not isPlaying(SEATED_PLAYERS,"Orange"))
            ) then
                broadcastToAll("All players have passed.\nThe year has ended, click on the Pass Year button!")
                CURRENT_SEASON = nil
            end
        end
    end,
    2,
    -1
)

function checkCockSide(cock)
    if (cock.getPosition()[1] > -21 and cock.getPosition()[1] < -16 and cock.getPosition()[3] > -3 and cock.getPosition()[3] < 7.5 and cock.getPosition()[2] > 0.9 and cock.getPosition()[2] < 1) then
        -- Cock is inside the track
        if cock.getPosition()[1] < -19 then
            return "Left"
        else
            return "Right"
        end
    else
        return nil
    end
end

function dealOneMama()
    self.clearButtons()
    self.createButton(start_button_parameters)
    broadcastToAll("Receive the resources from your Mama and Papa cards", {0,255,0})
    dealMamaPapa(SEATED_PLAYERS,1)
end

function dealTwoMama()
    self.clearButtons()
    self.createButton(start_button_parameters)
    broadcastToAll("Chose one of each Mama and Papa card and receive the resources from them", {0,255,0})
    dealMamaPapa(SEATED_PLAYERS,2)
end

function startTheGame()
    GAME_STARTED = true
    START_TIME = os.time()
    print(".\n.\n.\n")
    CURRENT_SEASON = "Spring"
    CURRENT_FIRST_PLAYER = setFirstPlayer(SEATED_PLAYERS)
    moveFirstPlayerToken(CURRENT_FIRST_PLAYER)
    initialPositionCock(SEATED_PLAYERS)
    initialPositionWorkers(SEATED_PLAYERS)
    initialPositionCork(SEATED_PLAYERS)
    initialPositionBottle(SEATED_PLAYERS)
    self.clearButtons()
    self.createButton(year_button_parameters)
    Wait.time(
        function()
            broadcastToAll("Starting the year "..CURRENT_YEAR.."\n It is spring, chose your wake up hour!")
            print("..."..CURRENT_FIRST_PLAYER.." will be the first player")
        end,
        2.5
    )
end

function endTheGame()
    if(checkWorkersWerePlaced(SEATED_PLAYERS)) then
        self.clearButtons()
        payResidual(SEATED_PLAYERS)
        local winners = checkWinner(SEATED_PLAYERS)
        print(".\n.\n.\n")
        if #winners == 1 then
            broadcastToAll(winners[1].." was the winner!",winners[1])
        else
            local win = ""
            for _,winner in ipairs(winners) do
                win = win.." "..winner
            end
            broadcastToAll("There is a tie between ["..win.." ]!\nUntie by Lira Value, then Wine Value and then Grape Value.", Table)
        end
        END_TIME = os.time()
        local duration = math.floor((END_TIME-START_TIME)/60)
        print("The game ended at the end of year "..CURRENT_YEAR.."\nIt has lasted for "..duration.." minutes.")
    else
        if(not winner) then
            broadcastToAll("Place all workers before ending the game",{r=255, g=0, b=0})
        end
    end
end

function passYear()
    if(checkWorkersWerePlaced(SEATED_PLAYERS)) then
        PASSING = true
        CURRENT_YEAR = CURRENT_YEAR+1
        print(".\n.\n.\n")
        broadcastToAll("Manually age your grape and wine tokens", {255,0,0})
        passFirstPlayerToken(SEATED_PLAYERS)
        initialPositionCock(SEATED_PLAYERS)
        initialPositionWorkers(SEATED_PLAYERS)
        checkPlayerCards(SEATED_PLAYERS)
        payResidual(SEATED_PLAYERS)
        CURRENT_SEASON = "Spring"
        Wait.time(
            function()
                PASSING = false
            end,
            1
        )
        Wait.time(

function bottleInResidualAreaNotCenter(bottle)
    if (((bottle.getPosition()[1]-16.9)^2 + (bottle.getPosition()[3]+1)^2)^0.5 > 1.04) and (((bottle.getPosition()[1]-16.9)^2 + (bottle.getPosition()[3]+1)^2)^0.5 < 2.9) then
        return true
    else
        return false
    end
end

function checkDegreeBottle(bottle)
    if (bottle.getPosition()[1] > 17 and bottle.getPosition()[3] > -1) then
        return(math.deg(math.atan(math.abs((bottle.getPosition()[3]+1)/(bottle.getPosition()[1]-17)))))
    elseif(bottle.getPosition()[1] < 17 and bottle.getPosition()[3] > -1) then
        return(180-math.deg(math.atan(math.abs((bottle.getPosition()[3]+1)/(bottle.getPosition()[1]-17)))))
    elseif(bottle.getPosition()[1] < 17 and bottle.getPosition()[3] < -1) then
        return(180+math.deg(math.atan(math.abs((bottle.getPosition()[3]+1)/(bottle.getPosition()[1]-17)))))
    elseif(bottle.getPosition()[1] > 17 and bottle.getPosition()[3] < -1) then
        return(360-math.deg(math.atan(math.abs((bottle.getPosition()[3]+1)/(bottle.getPosition()[1]-17)))))
    else
        return 0
    end
end

function checkResidualPosition(bottle)
    if bottleInResidualAreaNotCenter(bottle) then
        local degree = checkDegreeBottle(bottle)
        if degree >= 90 and degree < 162.6 then
            return 1
        elseif degree < 90 and degree >= 17.4 then
            return 2
        elseif (degree < 17.4 and degree > 0) or (degree <=360 and degree >= 306.9) then
            return 3
        elseif degree >= 233.1 and degree < 306.9 then
            return 4
        else
            return 5
        end
    else
        return 0
    end
end

function random(x, y)
    local u = 0 -- don't delete
    u = u + 1
    if x ~= nil and y ~= nil then
        return math.floor(x +(math.random(math.randomseed(os.time()+u))*999999 %y))
    else
        return math.floor((math.random(math.randomseed(os.time()+u))*100))
    end
end
